description: For sale: $260,000. Welcome home to this wonderful ranch style home in Brook Park.  When you enter the home you will be drawn to the windows with a great view of the private backyard full of mature trees.  The dining room has a vaulted ceiling with beams and beautiful floors.  The sunroom is a great place to soak up the sun and enjoy the scenery and abundant wildlife.  The kitchen is complete with stainless steel appliances and tons of storage and counter space. The owner's suite is on the main level along with another bedrm and full bath.  There is also an oversized mudroom/laundry room on the main level to complete your single level living.  When you move to the lower level you are again greet with plenty of natural light from the large windows.  There is a sitting room dining room combo as well as a full second kitchen.  The large bedrm has attached bath with jetted tub. The entire home has in-floor heat.  This lower level space does have access to the back yard.  Call today to schedule your showing!

Recently sold: $102,500. Tons of potential in this four bedroom, two bathroom home in Brook Park! Just an hour and a half outside of the Twin Cities in the Mora/Ogilvie area with relaxing views of the 8.43 acre lot it rests on!  Located within the Mora School District (ISD 332) close to Whited State Wildlife Mgmt Area and Berm Benders Raceway  just minutes to Hwy 65 or Hwy 23 for a quick commute! Enjoy 1,968  finished square feet of living space! The main level features a spacious living room, kitchen with ample countertop and cabinet space and dining room. The upper level has three bedrooms--one of which is the master suite w/a private ¾ bathroom plus another full bathroom!  The lower level has a family room and fourth bedroom! Sellers just redid some flooring on the main two levels, painted some rooms, installed a new septic and well pump. Quick drive to Mora from this location. Some TLC needed yet!

For more information on this charming Brook Park home for sale contact Chuck Carstensen with Re/Max Results at 612-290-3809 today!
